#. <section class="sutta" id="sn6.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn6.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The Appeal"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 5. Aññatarabrahmasutta → aparādiṭṭhisuttaṃ (bj, s1-3) | aparādiṭṭhi (pts1)
msgctxt "sn6.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Aññatarabrahmasutta"
msgstr "5. A Certain Brahmā"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn6.5:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena aññatarassa brahmuno evarūpaṃ pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ "
"uppannaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""
"Now at that time a certain Brahmā had the following harmful misconception:"

msgctxt "sn6.5:1.3"
msgid "“natthi so samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā yo idha āgaccheyyā”ti."
msgstr "“No ascetic or brahmin can come here!”"

msgctxt "sn6.5:1.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā tassa brahmuno cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya—seyyathāpi "
"nāma balavā puriso … pe … tasmiṃ brahmaloke pāturahosi."
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha knew what that Brahmā was thinking. As easily as a strong "
"person would extend or contract their arm, he vanished from Jeta’s Grove and "
"reappeared in that Brahmā realm."

msgctxt "sn6.5:1.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā tassa brahmuno upari vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisīdi tejodhātuṃ "
"samāpajjitvā."
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha sat cross-legged in the air above that Brahmā, having "
"entered upon the fire element."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.315"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato mahāmoggallānassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Venerable Mahāmoggallāna thought:"

msgctxt "sn6.5:2.2"
msgid "“kahaṃ nu kho bhagavā etarahi viharatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Where is the Buddha staying at present?”"

#. VAR: mahāmoggallāno → mahāmoggalāno (mr)
msgctxt "sn6.5:2.3"
msgid ""
"Addasā kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhagavantaṃ dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena "
"atikkantamānusakena tassa brahmuno upari vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisinnaṃ "
"tejodhātuṃ samāpannaṃ."
msgstr ""
"With clairvoyance that is purified and superhuman, he saw the Buddha seated "
"cross-legged in the air above that Brahmā, having entered upon the fire "
"element."

msgctxt "sn6.5:2.4"
msgid ""
"Disvāna—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ vā bāhaṃ pasāreyya, "
"pasāritaṃ vā bāhaṃ samiñjeyya; evameva—jetavane antarahito tasmiṃ brahmaloke "
"pāturahosi."
msgstr ""
"Then, as easily as a strong person would extend or contract their arm, he "
"vanished from Jeta’s Grove and reappeared in that Brahmā realm."

#. VAR: nissāya → upanissāya (si)
msgctxt "sn6.5:2.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno puratthimaṃ disaṃ nissāya tassa brahmuno "
"upari vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisīdi tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā nīcataraṃ bhagavato."
msgstr ""
"Then Mahāmoggallāna—positioning himself in the east, below the Buddha—sat "
"cross-legged in the air above that Brahmā, having entered upon the fire "
"element."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.145"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato mahākassapassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Venerable Mahākassapa …"

msgctxt "sn6.5:3.2"
msgid "“kahaṃ nu kho bhagavā etarahi viharatī”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn6.5:3.3"
msgid "Addasā kho āyasmā mahākassapo bhagavantaṃ dibbena cakkhunā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn6.5:3.4"
msgid ""
"disvāna—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso … pe … evameva—jetavane antarahito "
"tasmiṃ brahmaloke pāturahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn6.5:3.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā mahākassapo dakkhiṇaṃ disaṃ nissāya tassa brahmuno upari "
"vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisīdi tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā nīcataraṃ bhagavato."
msgstr "positioned himself in the south …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.316"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato mahākappinassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Venerable Mahākappina …"

msgctxt "sn6.5:4.2"
msgid "“kahaṃ nu kho bhagavā etarahi viharatī”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn6.5:4.3"
msgid ""
"Addasā kho āyasmā mahākappino bhagavantaṃ dibbena cakkhunā … pe … tejodhātuṃ "
"samāpannaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn6.5:4.4"
msgid "Disvāna—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn6.5:4.5"
msgid "evameva—jetavane antarahito tasmiṃ brahmaloke pāturahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn6.5:4.6"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā mahākappino pacchimaṃ disaṃ nissāya tassa brahmuno upari "
"vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisīdi tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā nīcataraṃ bhagavato."
msgstr "positioned himself in the west …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:5.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato anuruddhassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "and Venerable Anuruddha …"

msgctxt "sn6.5:5.2"
msgid "“kahaṃ nu kho bhagavā etarahi viharatī”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn6.5:5.3"
msgid "Addasā kho āyasmā anuruddho … pe … tejodhātuṃ samāpannaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn6.5:5.4"
msgid ""
"Disvāna—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso … pe … tasmiṃ brahmaloke pāturahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn6.5:5.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā anuruddho uttaraṃ disaṃ nissāya tassa brahmuno upari vehāsaṃ "
"pallaṅkena nisīdi tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā nīcataraṃ bhagavato."
msgstr ""
"positioned himself in the north, below the Buddha, sitting cross-legged in "
"the air above that Brahmā, having entered upon the fire element."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:6.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno taṃ brahmānaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "Then Mahāmoggallāna addressed that Brahmā in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:7.1"
msgid "“Ajjāpi te āvuso sā diṭṭhi,"
msgstr "“Sir, do you still have the same view"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:7.2"
msgid "Yā te diṭṭhi pure ahu;"
msgstr "that you had in the past?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:7.3"
msgid "Passasi vītivattantaṃ,"
msgstr "Or do you see the radiance"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:7.4"
msgid "Brahmaloke pabhassaran”ti."
msgstr "transcending the Brahmā realm?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:8.1"
msgid "“Na me mārisa sā diṭṭhi,"
msgstr "“Good sir, I don’t have that view"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:8.2"
msgid "yā me diṭṭhi pure ahu;"
msgstr "that I had in the past."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:8.3"
msgid "Passāmi vītivattantaṃ,"
msgstr "I see the radiance"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:8.4"
msgid "brahmaloke pabhassaraṃ;"
msgstr "transcending the Brahmā realm."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:8.5"
msgid "Svāhaṃ ajja kathaṃ vajjaṃ,"
msgstr "So how could I say today"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:8.6"
msgid "ahaṃ niccomhi sassato”ti."
msgstr "that I am permanent and eternal?”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.146"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.317"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:9.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā taṃ brahmānaṃ saṃvejetvā—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso "
"samiñjitaṃ vā bāhaṃ pasāreyya, pasāritaṃ vā bāhaṃ samiñjeyya; evameva—tasmiṃ "
"brahmaloke antarahito jetavane pāturahosi."
msgstr ""
"Having inspired a sense of awe in the Brahmā, as easily as a strong person "
"would extend or contract their arm, the Buddha vanished from the Brahmā "
"realm and reappeared in Jeta’s Grove."

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.2"
msgid "Atha kho so brahmā aññataraṃ brahmapārisajjaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then that Brahmā addressed a member of his retinue:"

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.3"
msgid ""
"“ehi tvaṃ, mārisa, yenāyasmā mahāmoggallāno tenupasaṅkama; upasaṅkamitvā "
"āyasmantaṃ mahāmoggallānaṃ evaṃ vadehi:"
msgstr "“Please, good sir, go up to Venerable Mahāmoggallāna and say to him:"

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.4"
msgid ""
"‘atthi nu kho, mārisa moggallāna, aññepi tassa bhagavato sāvakā "
"evaṃmahiddhikā evaṃmahānubhāvā;"
msgstr ""
"‘Moggallāna my good sir, are there any other disciples of the Buddha who "
"have power and might"

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.5"
msgid "seyyathāpi bhavaṃ moggallāno kassapo kappino anuruddho’”ti?"
msgstr ""
"comparable to the masters Moggallāna, Kassapa, Kappina, and Anuruddha?’”"

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.6"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, mārisā”ti kho so brahmapārisajjo tassa brahmuno paṭissutvā yenāyasmā "
"mahāmoggallāno tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ mahāmoggallānaṃ "
"etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"“Yes, good sir,” replied that retinue member. He went to Moggallāna and "
"asked as instructed."

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.7"
msgid ""
"“atthi nu kho, mārisa moggallāna, aññepi tassa bhagavato sāvakā "
"evaṃmahiddhikā evaṃmahānubhāvā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.8"
msgid "seyyathāpi bhavaṃ moggallāno kassapo kappino anuruddho”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn6.5:9.9"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno taṃ brahmapārisajjaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "Then Mahāmoggallāna addressed that member of Brahmā’s retinue in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:10.1"
msgid "“Tevijjā iddhipattā ca,"
msgstr "“There are many disciples of the Buddha"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:10.2"
msgid "cetopariyāyakovidā;"
msgstr "who have the three knowledges,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:10.3"
msgid "Khīṇāsavā arahanto,"
msgstr "and have attained psychic power, expert in reading minds,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:10.4"
msgid "bahū buddhassa sāvakā”ti."
msgstr "they’re perfected ones with defilements ended.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:11.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho so brahmapārisajjo āyasmato mahāmoggallānassa bhāsitaṃ abhinanditvā "
"anumoditvā yena so brahmā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā taṃ brahmānaṃ "
"etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then that member of Brahmā’s retinue, having approved and agreed with what "
"Mahāmoggallāna said, went to that Brahmā and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn6.5:11.2"
msgid "“āyasmā, mārisa, mahāmoggallāno evamāha:"
msgstr "“Good sir, Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said this:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:12.1"
msgid "‘Tevijjā iddhipattā ca,"
msgstr "‘There are many disciples of the Buddha"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:12.2"
msgid "cetopariyāyakovidā;"
msgstr "who have the three knowledges,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:12.3"
msgid "Khīṇāsavā arahanto,"
msgstr "and have attained psychic power, expert in reading minds,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.5:12.4"
msgid "bahū buddhassa sāvakā’”ti."
msgstr "they’re perfected ones with defilements ended.’”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.5:13.1"
msgid "Idamavoca so brahmapārisajjo."
msgstr "That’s what that member of Brahmā’s retinue said."

msgctxt "sn6.5:13.2"
msgid "Attamano ca so brahmā tassa brahmapārisajjassa bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti."
msgstr ""
"Satisfied, that Brahmā was happy with what the member of his retinue said."
